174 A.3d 516 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. JACQUIM LOVELY, A/K/A JACQUIN LOVLEY, YASIM ANDERSON, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-157 September Term 2017

079341 October 16, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004025-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
